 or srap turning 65 if you are still an active employee nothing changes however if you are a retiree and turning age 65 your health benefits will change see retiree health benefits in the medical & life section to learn more download the retirement checklist or contact stanford benefits text too small if you re having trouble reading this page find out how to increase the size of the text resources view your retiree healthcare kit benefits overview online presentation streaming flash presentation updated 02 21 12 retirement plan refresher online presentation streaming flash presentation updated 02 01 12 retirement checklist home benefits overview medical & life retirement resource library contacts mybenefits site map how to use this site human resources stanford university stanford university terms of use copyright complaints document download
